title: Parantha Alley - Food Stall
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Indian parantha stuffed with choice of fillings. Vegan choices such as: carrot and coconut, potatoes and peas, sugar almond cardamom, radish. Location is Smorgasburg's outdoor food market in Williamsburg. Also Sundays in Dumbo at the old tobacco warehouse in Brooklyn bridge park.
